---
title: Double Sichuan-Glazed Pork Rissoles with Sesame Fries & Asian Slaw
description: How to improve pork rissoles? Toss them in our mild Sichuan garlic paste, of course! It adds loads of flavour and that saucy touch that makes every mouthful a delight. Fries with crisp sesame seeds and slaw coated in Japanese dressing seal the deal.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67b2bd16a27a53fcaa21eb1b-cba4ebf7.jpeg
